Floating Plastic Bottle Collector 
Research & Develop a Design on “Floating Plastic Bottle Collector” 
designed to collect plastic bottles from lakes and rivers. 
● Dimensions: Max 280cm L / 150cm W / 90cm H. 
● Collection Capacity: Minimum 100 bottles per cycle. 
● Collection System: Conveyor-based bottle intake mechanism. 
● Material: Lightweight floating materials. 
● Durability: Suitable for continuous water exposure. 
● Waste Handling: Easy unloading system. 
